videos.description: The Golden Eagles' Markus Howard drives and lays it in.
videos.headline: Marquette's Howard with a reverse layup

videos.description: Off the rebound, Quentin Goodin takes the ball down the court and soars for a one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Xavier's Goodin goes coast-to-coast to throw the hammer down

videos.description: Quentin Goodin goes in for the drive and somehow wraps the ball around his defenders, finding Kerem Kanter who lays it in.
videos.headline: Goodin's sweet pass sets up Musketeers' layup

videos.description: On a layup, Xavier's J.P. Macura hand gets caught in the net and it rips, causing a delay of game.
videos.headline: Game is stopped due to ripped net

videos.description: J.P. Macura bounce passes it to Tyrique Jones who jumps up for a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Two -handed jam for Xaviers' Jones

videos.description: Trevon Bluiett drains two-point jumper to get his 2,000th career point, and becomes the 5th player in Xavier history to do so.
videos.headline: Xavier's Bluiett hits 2,000 career points

videos.description: Paul Scruggs intercepts a Marquette pass and lobs it up to Quentin Goodin, who throws down a one-handed hammer.
videos.headline: The Musketeers' Goodin throws down for an alley-oop jam
